  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'=
>Assault
  Pods are used to launch boarding parties against nearby enemy ships or ba=
ses.
  The armed boarding parties travel a short distance to a target that has <=
span
  class=3DGramE>it&#8217;s</span> shields lowered sufficiently. On reaching=
 the
  target, the attackers board the enemy vessel and fight with the defenders=
.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'=
>Assault
  Pods also serve as defensive forces if a ship or base is boarded by an
  attacker.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'=
>Assault
  Pods can be launched against a target when:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list=
:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;
  mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><span style=3D'mso-l=
ist:
  Ignore'>&middot;<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-langu=
age:
  EN-GB'>the target is in range<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpLast style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;
  mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><span style=3D'mso-l=
ist:
  Ignore'>&middot;<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-langu=
age:
  EN-GB'>the target has low shields<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'=
>Once an
  assault pod has been launched it is unavailable for a while until it
  regenerates a new boarding party.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'=
>Note that
  assault pods can be shot down by Point <span class=3DSpellE>Defense</span>
  weapons while in transit to a target.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'=
>Assault
  Pods are also used by pirates to launch raids against enemy bases or
  colonies. In this case, when the assault pod reaches the target they board
  (for bases) or invade (for colonies) the target and fight with any defend=
ers.
  If the attackers win the battle they loot the target, carrying away money,
  resources or other loot.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
